    "body" : "<p>Its simple only one line code is needed for this.\nif <code>String A = scanner.nextLine();</code>\nthen you need to write this to display the string with this first letter capitalized.</p>\n\n<p><code>System.out.println(A.substring(0, 1).toUpperCase() + A.substring(1));</code></p>\n\n<p>And its done now.</p>\n"
