    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>My functional approach. its capstilise first character in sentence after whitescape in whole paragraph.</p>\n\n<p>For capatilising only first character of the word just remove <strong>.split(\" \")</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>           b.name.split(\" \")\n                 .filter { !it.isEmpty() }\n                 .map { it.substring(0, 1).toUpperCase() \n                 +it.substring(1).toLowerCase() }\n                  .joinToString(\" \")\n</code></pre>\n"
